Ingredients
* peppermint peeps
* hot chocolate powder
* milk
* creme de menthe

Directions
* heat 1 cup milk to nearly a boil, remove skin if it forms, turn off heat
* add 3 Tablespoons hot chocolate powder (or otherwise as directed by brand), whisk
* in mug place 2 ounces creme de menthe and 1-2 peeps
* pour hot chocolate over peeps and liquor

Notes
* peeps optional
